item.title: Our Wedding
item.description: We’re getting married on September 14, 2019 at 11:00 AM. We’re excited to have you join us! Please let us know if you can make it by August 15. More information can be found below: Day Of When and where The wedding will be held on September 14, 2019 at Camp Plymouth in Ludlow, VT. The park opens at 10:00 AM, with the ceremony starting at 11:00 AM, followed by a reception.
